                  ለተአምርኪ ፡ ጽጌ ፡ አሃሊ ፡ እሙ ፡
                  ማኅሌተ ፡ ጽጌ ፡ ዘይሰመይ ፡ ስሙ ፡
                  </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>(<locus target="#4r #4v #5r #5v" facs="005 006 007"/> are written in a different hand on an inserted leaf), arranged for the days of the week. In each case a piece of thread has been sewn into the upper fore edge.
